Peter Jones ya fusata da janyewar Holly Willoughby daga kwangilarsa ta fam miliyan 11
Peter Jones, wanda ya fito a shirin talabijin na Dragons' Den, ya fusata sosai da ya ji cewa Holly Willoughby za ta yi murabus daga kasuwancinta na fam miliyan 11 domin mayar da hankali kan sabuwar hulda da Marks da Spencer da ITV
Holly Willoughby ba ta da lokaci don alamar kayan haɗi da kayan gida mai suna Truly.
An kwatanta ayyukan da Gwyneth Paltrow ke yi da Goop.
A safiyar yau ne mai shekaru 37 ta sanar da ficewarta ta shafin Instagram.
Shawarar da Holly Willoughby ta yanke na barin wata alama mai kyau ta rayuwa don mayar da hankali kan sabon haɗin gwiwa tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV ya fusata Peter Jones, tauraron Dragons Den.
Majiyoyin sun ce, Peter Jones ya fusata sosai lokacin da wata shahararriyar mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen talabijin ta sanar a wani taron firgita a ranar Talata a fadarsa ta kasuwanci da ke Marlow, Buckinghamshire cewa saboda sabbin kwangila da suka kai fam miliyan 1.5 ba za ta sami lokacin da za ta yi aiki da alamar kayan aikin gida da kayan gida na Trula ba.
An kwatanta wannan kamfani da Goop, wanda Gwyneth Paltrow ke da shi, kuma an ce zai ninka dukiyar Holly Willoughby da aka kiyasta ya kai fam miliyan 11.
Bayan Holly Willoughby mai shekaru 37 ta sanar da shawarar barin alamar Trula a shafin Instagram, Peter Jones ya bar Burtaniya, yana zuwa daya daga cikin gidajen hutun sa.
Majiyar ta ce, "Marca Truly ita ce babbar hanyar da Holly Willoughby ke bi.
Ta san cewa wannan ita ce rayuwarta kuma tana son ta ci gaba da yin hakan har shekaru da yawa.
Wannan shawarar ta sa duk wanda ya shiga cikin lamarin ya yi mamaki.
Babu wanda ya gaskanta abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, da yake kusan shiga kasuwa.
Akwai kaya a cikin shagon a Marlow da aka shirya don sayarwa.
Masana sun yi imanin cewa barin wannan jarumar shirin na This Morning da kuma daya daga cikin fitattun jaruman Birtaniya zai iya jawo wa kamfanin asarar miliyoyin fam saboda zuba jari mai yawa a kayayyakin  daga matashin kai zuwa kyandirori zuwa tufafi da kayan gida  da kuma kara jinkirta shiga kasuwa.
