Ambaliyar ruwa da ta faru sanadiyyar guguwar Rosa ta yi barazanar fara samun Phoenix, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City (mai yiwuwa ta shafi yankunan da fari ya shafa)
Ba kasafai ake samun wani yanayi mai zafi da zai kai jihar Arizona ba, amma zai iya zuwa farkon mako mai zuwa, saboda ambaliyar ruwan da ta biyo bayan guguwar Rosa tana tafiya a cikin hamadar Kudu maso Yammacin Amurka, yana haifar da barazanar ambaliyar ruwa.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Kasa ta ba da gargadin yiwuwar ambaliyar ruwa a yammacin Arizona, kudu da gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah a ranar Litinin da Talata, ciki har da biranen Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
Rahotanni sun nuna cewa a ranar Talata Rosa za ta wuce Phoenix kai tsaye, kuma za ta fara ruwan sama a ranar Litinin da yamma.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Phoenix ta ce a shafinta na Twitter, tun shekara ta 1950, hadari 10 ne kawai suka kai matsayin guguwa ko kuma yanayi mai zafi a cikin nisan mil 200 daga birnin Phoenix.
A shekara ta 1967, guguwar Katrina ta kai kusan mil 40 daga iyakar jihar Arizona.
A cikin wasu wurare a yankin Mogollon Rim na Arizona, za a iya samun ruwan sama mai tsawon inci 15.
A sauran yankunan hamada na Kudu maso Yamma  ciki har da tsakiyar Rocky Mountains da Great Basin  ana sa ran samun ruwan sama daga 2.5 zuwa 5 cm, kuma a wasu yankuna har zuwa 10 cm.
Ga waɗanda ba sa cikin yankunan da ambaliyar take aukuwa, ruwan sama da ke tafe bayan guguwar Rosa zai iya kawo sauƙi, domin yankin ya daɗe yana fama da fari.
Ko da yake ambaliyar ruwa tana da haɗari sosai, amma za ta taimaka wajen magance matsalar fari a yankin kudu maso yammacin ƙasar.
A cewar wani rahoto da aka yi a dandalin weather.com, U.S. Drought Monitor ya ce kusan kashi 40 cikin ɗari na yankin Arizona suna fama da fari mai tsanani.
Guguwar Rosa za ta fara kaiwa yankin California da ke Mexico.
A safiyar ranar Lahadi Rosa ta ci gaba da motsawa da karfin guguwa, tana kaiwa gudun kilomita 137 a awa daya.
Guguwar ta haɗu da ruwan sanyi na Pacific Ocean, wanda ke sa ta zama mai rauni.
Ana hasashen cewa za ta yi iska mai ƙarfi a Mexico da yammacin Litinin ko kuma da yamma.
Ruwan sama mai yawa da aka yi a wasu wurare a ƙasar Mexico zai iya jawo ambaliyar ruwa.
A wani yanki daga yankin California zuwa arewa maso yammacin jihar Sonora, weather.com ta ce ana sa ran samun ruwan sama mai tsawon inci 7 zuwa 15 amma zai iya kaiwa inci 25.
Bayan haka, guguwar Rosa za ta ratsa Mexico zuwa arewa a matsayin guguwar da za ta kai iyakar jihar Arizona a safiyar Talata, kuma za ta koma kudancin Utah da yammacin Talata.
Abubuwan da ke kawo hadari mafi tsanani daga guguwar Rosa ko kuma daga cikinta su ne ruwan sama mai yawa a yankin California, arewa maso yammacin Sonora, da kuma hamadar kudu maso yammacin Amirka, in ji National Hurricane Center.
An yi hasashen cewa ruwan sama zai jawo ambaliyar ruwa da za ta iya kashe mutane da kuma gurɓata hamada da kuma kwararar laka a duwatsu.
