Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take baiwa binciken AI
Kai-Fu Lee, mai saka jari kuma masanin ilimin kere kere wanda ke aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple, ya ce, tare da karuwar ayyukan China a wannan yanki, Amurka ta kamata ta ninka kudaden da take kashewa a binciken AI.
Wannan bayanin yana da alaƙa da tallan da aka buga game da ilimin kere kere ta hanyar hukumomin gwamnati daban-daban na Amurka, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabara ta AI.
A shekarar da ta gabata ne kasar Sin ta bayyana shirin ta na zama kasa mafi inganci a fannin kera kere-kere a duniya nan da shekarar 2030.
Kai-Fu Lee ya ce: "Abin da ya kamata mu fara yi shi ne ninka kasafin kudin da muke kashewa wajen gudanar da bincike kan ilimin kere kere.
A wata hira da aka yi da shi a wannan makon, ya kuma ce ninka kudaden zai ninka damar da za a samu wani ci gaba a fannin kere-kere a Amurka.
Lee, wanda littafinsa mai suna AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order ya fito a wannan watan daga Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne shugaban kamfanin Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kera kere a kasar Sin, wanda aka fi sani da Face++.
A shekarun 1980s, Kai-Fu Lee ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon don ƙirƙirar tsarin AI wanda ya doke mafi kyawun ɗan wasan Amurka a lokacin Othello. Daga nan sai ya zama babban jami'in Microsoft Research kuma ya kasance shugaban kamfanin Google na China.
Lee ya yaba da nasarar da gwamnatin Amurka ta samu a baya, kamar gasar da Hukumar Nazarin Harkokin Tsaro ta DARPA ta shirya don samar da zane-zane na mutummutumi, kuma ya yi tambaya game da lokacin da za a sake buga gasar, saboda ya yi imanin cewa zai taimaka wajen gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
Kamar yadda Kai-Fu Lee ya ce, masu bincike a Amirka sukan yi ƙoƙari sosai don su sami tallafin gwamnati.
"Ba kasar Sin ce ke karbar mafi kyawun malamanmu ba, amma kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, Facebook da Google da kuma wasu kamfanonin fasaha sun ɗauki manyan masana kimiyya su yi aiki a kan aikin AI.
Lee ya ce, sauye-sauyen da aka yi a manufofin shige da fice na iya taimaka wa Amurka wajen bunkasa AI.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba wa masu aikin kere kere katin aiki ta atomatik idan sun sami digiri na biyu", in ji shi.
A watan Yuli na 2017, majalisar kasar Sin ta fitar da wani shiri na samar da wata sabuwar fasahar kere kere.
Lee ya ce, National Natural Science Foundation of China tana ba da kudade ga malamai a makarantu kamar yadda National Science Foundation da sauran kungiyoyin gwamnati ke ba da kudade ga masana kimiyya a Amurka, amma ingancin ayyukan ilimi a kasar Sin ya kasa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Haɗin Kai ta Artificial Intelligence don shiga cikin masana'antu da abokan hulɗa a kimiyya, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Kwamitin Zaɓin kan Artificial Intelligence.
A wannan watan, DARPA ta sanar da cewa ta ba da dala biliyan biyu don wani shiri da ake kira AI Next.
Gidauniyar Kimiyya ta kasa tana zuba jari sama da dala biliyan 100 a kowace shekara a binciken AI.
A lokaci guda kuma, shirin Amirka na kafa kwamiti na 'yan Adam don kāre fasaha ta wucin gadi bai ci gaba ba har tsawon watanni.
