Taron zaben Trump a jihar West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron zaɓe a Wheeling, West Virginia, a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin taron zaɓe biyar da Trump ya shirya gudanarwa a mako mai zuwa, tare da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da wannan kuri'ar da ta tabbatar da dakatar da zabensa a kan kujerar da ke gaban kotun kolin, Trump na neman samun goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe a tsakiyar mulkinsa, saboda 'yan Republican na iya rasa iko a majalisar dokoki lokacin da aka kada kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron zaben Trump a yammacin Virginia kuma a ina za a iya kallon sa a yanar gizo?
Za a yi taron zaben shugaban kasa a Wheeling, West Virginia a karfe 7 na dare a yau Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za a iya kallon taron zaben Trump a West Virginia a kai tsaye a YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai yi magana game da sauraron karar da aka yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh a wannan makon, wanda ya faru ne a cikin yanayi mai matukar damuwa game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i, da kuma kuri'ar da majalisar dattijai ke shirin kada a dakatar da zaben na tsawon mako guda, yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin taron zaben shine don tallafawa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar babban zabe a watan Nuwamba.
Don haka, yakin neman zaben shugaba Trump na mako mai zuwa yana da manufa guda biyar, wanda shine "tallafa masu sa kai da magoya baya don taimakawa 'yan Republican wajen karewa da kuma kara rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai".
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki babban abu ne a cikin jadawalin shugaban kasa, kuma a lokacin da yawon bude ido ya fi zafi, zai ziyarci jihohi da yawa", in ji mai magana da yawun kamfen din Trump, wanda bai yarda a bayyana sunansa ba  Reuters.
Taron zaben da za a yi a gidan wasan Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling a yau, zai iya jan hankalin magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, da kuma kafofin yada labarai daga Pittsburgh da West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar, Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia  jihar da ya lashe ta da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016  a karo na biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jihar West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya yi kasa a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey idan shugaban ya zo ya goyi bayansa a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia  Reuters.
