Bayan an yi wasanni uku a rana ɗaya, wasan rukuni huɗu da ake yi a ranar Asabar da rana zai iya zama abin da gasar Ryder Cup take bukata.
Wannan motsi na motsa jiki yana da cikakkiyar ra'ayi na wasanni, amma wanda masu tsere suka gaskata, musamman a wasanni kamar wannan.
To, menene irin wannan motsi a yanzu?
"Sun yi gaba da maki shida, amma yanzu suna gaba da maki hudu, don haka ina ganin muna da ɗan ci gaba", in ji Jordan Spieth.
A bayyane yake cewa Turai tana da maki hudu a gaba, amma akwai maki 12 da za a samu.
Amma, Spieth ya ce, 'yan Amurkawa suna da kwarin gwiwa kuma suna da misalai masu kyau, musamman a cikin Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma kowannensu ya sami maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Spieth yana da haɗari a kowane fanni kuma yana kafa misali.
Muryar murmushi ta kara daɗa ƙarfi yayin da yake ci gaba da zagaye, yana cin nasara a wasan da ya yi da Thomas.
A lokacin da ya buga kwallo a kasa, wanda ya ba su nasara da ci 15 a raga, sai ya yi ihu kamar yadda yake nuna cewa Amurka tana cikin wasan.
"Kawai ka mai da hankali da kuma damu da wasan ka", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne abin da kowane daga cikin 'yan wasan ya rage.
Akwai ramuka 18 da za a ci.
'Yan wasan da suka ci kwallo fiye da Spieth da Thomas a kwanaki biyu da suka gabata, su ne Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, tarihin gasar Ryder Cup.
Wasu ma'aurata masu ban mamaki amma masu kyau daga ƙungiyar Turai sun ci hudu daga cikin hudu kuma ba su yi kuskure ba.
'Yan matan Hollywood ne kawai ma'aurata da ba su yi bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, amma sun guje wa bogey a ranar Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da yamma da kuma baya tara a ranar Jumma'a.
Yadda suke wasa da kuma yadda suke ganin makamashi yana gudana zuwa da kuma daga cikin taron jama'a ya nuna cewa dole ne a doke 'yan wasan a ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani dan wasa mafi kyau fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari wanda zai iya rufe yiwuwar nasarar kungiyar Turai a Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau idan suka yi wasa a ramuka daban-daban a lokaci guda.
Amma ba a san ko 'yan wasan Turai za su yi nasara ba.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi saurin kashe Sergio Garcia, gwarzon dan wasan kwallon kafa na safe, lokacin da aka hada shi da Alex Noren.
Bogey da kuma ninki biyu a gaban tara sun kori Spaniard da Swede zuwa rami wanda ba za su taba fita ba.
A ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai iya taimaka maka ka fita daga cikin rami.
Ƙungiyoyin ƙwallon ƙafa da ƙwallon ƙafa suna da ban sha'awa saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa, shawarwarin da ba su bayar ba, da kuma yadda za a iya canza dabarun a cikin wani lokaci.
Turai ta yi fice a matsayin kungiya kuma ta samu gagarumar nasara a rana ta karshe, amma wasan hudu ya kuma nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da karfin gwiwa, wanda wasu musamman a Amurka suka yi shakkarsa.
Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a wasan karshe na gasar Ryder Cup.
Turai ta samu gagarumar nasara a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder bayan da ta yi nasara da ci 10-6 a wasannin hudu da hudu da Amurka ta buga a ranar Asabar.
Wani dimbin mutane  Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari  sun yi nasara a wasan, inda suka ci Tiger Woods da ya yi gwagwarmaya, wanda ya kara maki hudu a gasar Le Golf National.
A kokarin da kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Turai ta Thomas Bjorn ke yi na rike kambin da ta rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta yi nasara a kan kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Amurka a wasan kwallon kafa na safe, inda ta lashe wasan da ci 3-1.
Amurka ta yi nasara a wasanni hudu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya sake dawowa ba.
Don ci gaba da lashe gasar, tawagar Jim Furyk za ta samu maki takwas daga cikin 12 da za a yi a ranar Lahadi.
Fleetwood ita ce ta farko da ta fara buga gasar Turai da ta ci kwallaye hudu a jere, yayin da ita da Molinari (wanda aka kira Molliwood bayan wasan karshen mako) su ne biyu a cikin tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da suka ci kwallaye hudu a wasanni hudu na farko.
Bayan sun murkushe Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallon kafa, sun doke Woods da kuma dan wasan Amurka, Bryson Dechambeau, don samun karin fifiko da hudu.
Woods, wanda ya gaji da wasannin biyu da ya buga a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu halayen gwaninta, amma ya rasa wasanni 19 cikin 29 a wasanni hudu da hudu, kuma ya yi nasara sau bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ba ya cikin wasan kwallon kafa na safe, ya sake komawa Henry Stenson a cikin wasan kwallon kafa na hudu don ya doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka  da ke matsayi na 1 da 3 a duniya.
Amma, wasu abubuwa sun faru a wannan rana mai sanyi da ke kudu maso yammacin birnin Paris.
Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, wadanda suka lashe gasar sau uku, sun kafa misali ga Amurkawa, inda suka ci maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
