Kit, wanda ya yi aure kwanan nan da matarsa a wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, mai shekaru 31, Rose Leslie, ya ce yana jin "daɗi" game da wannan batun.
"Ni kaina ina jin daɗi sosai a wannan lokacin" "Ina muka yi kuskure game da namiji?"
