A ranar Asabar, 'yar majalisar wakilai ta Amurka, Maxine Waters ta yi watsi da zargin cewa wani a cikin tawagarta ya sanya bayanan sirri na sanatoci uku na Republican a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisa.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Democrat a Los Angeles ya tabbatar da cewa masana da shafukan yanar gizo masu alaka da masu tsattsauran ra'ayi ne suka yi zargin.
"Karya, karya da karya mafi muni", Waters ta bayyana a wata sanarwa a shafinta na Twitter.
Bayanan da aka fitar sun hada da adiresoshin gida da lambobin waya na Sanata Lindsey Graham na South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch na Utah.
Wani mutum da ba a san ko shi wane ne ya wallafa wannan labarin a shafin yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis a lokacin da wani kwamitin majalisar dattijai ke sauraron tuhumar cin zarafin jima'i da aka yi wa wanda aka zaba a kotun kolin Amurka, Brett Kavanaugh.
