A cikin fim din Johnny English: K.O.  mai lalata da Rowan Atkinson
Neman nassoshi game da Brexit a cikin kowane sabon fim mai taken Burtaniya ya zama al'ada, kuma wannan ya zama daidai da sabon ɓangaren fim ɗin fim ɗin Johnny English, wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya dawo gidajen kallo a 2011 tare da Johnny English: Reactivation.
Shin wannan baƙar magana game da yadda muke da rashin bege za ta zama sabon kayan da ƙasar ke fitarwa?
Ko ta yaya, mai ban mamaki, mai fuskar roba, Johnny English mara kyau ya sake samun lasisin yin wasan kwaikwayo  sunansa fiye da komai yana nuna cewa shi mai ban dariya ne mai ban dariya wanda aka tsara don masu sauraron ba Turanci ba.
Shi ne, ba shakka, wani dan leken asiri mai ban tsoro wanda duk da irin son da yake da shi na glamorous, yana da wani abu daga Inspector Clouseau, da yatsan Jasi Fasoli da kuma wani abu daga mutumin da ya kara waƙar waƙa a cikin mawaki na Chariots of Fire a bikin bude gasar Olympics ta London a shekarar 2012.
A baya, shi ma matafiyi ne kuma mutum ne mai ban mamaki a duniya  Atkinson ya taɓa yin fim a cikin tallace-tallace na Barclaycard da aka manta da su a talabijin, inda ya bar rikici a baya.
A cikin sabon fim ɗin Johnny English, akwai wani abu ko biyu da ya kamata mu lura da su.
Na ji daɗin wannan sashen da Johnny English yake zuwa jirgi mai saukar ungulu da rigar yaƙi na zamanin dā, kuma yana saka kwalkwali da ke sa ƙafafunsa su riƙa bugawa.
A kan allon, Atkinson yana da kyauta ga wasan kwaikwayo na jiki, amma jin dadin jin dadi yana da ƙananan ƙananan kuma ba dole ba, musamman ma yanzu da manyan fina-finai kamar 007 da Mission Impossible suna ba da kayan wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin ɓangare na fim.
Abubuwan ban dariya sun fi dacewa da yara fiye da manya. Ina tsammanin Johnny English ba shi da kwarewa da kuma daidaituwa kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a cikin fina-finai na Jasi Bean.
Kuma abin da aka saba yi a ko yaushe shi ne cewa Birtaniya na cikin matsala.
Wani dan leken asiri ya shiga cikin manyan jami'an leken asirin Birtaniya, inda ya bayyana sunayen dukkan jami'an leken asirin Birtaniya da ke aiki a yankin, abin takaici ga jami'in da ke aiki, Kevin Eldon, wanda ba shi da wani muhimmin matsayi.
Wannan shine ƙarshen ƙarshen baƙin ciki na firaministan kasar, wanda shine mai ban sha'awa, wanda aka ɓata, wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga rashin jin daɗi saboda rashin amincewar siyasa: Emma Thompson tana yin duk abin da ta iya don yin Theresa May, amma rubutun bai ba ta damar shimfida fuka-fuki ba.
Masu ba ta shawara a hukumar leken asirin sun sanar da ita cewa saboda bayyana asalin dukkan 'yan leken asirin da ke aiki, za ta sake dawo da daya daga cikin jami'an da suka yi ritaya.
Wannan yana nufin Johnny English wanda ba shi da kwarewa a cikin kansa, yanzu yana aiki a matsayin malami a wata makarantar sakandare, yana ba da darussan da ba a san shi ba game da yadda za a zama wakili na sirri  wasu gags masu kyau a lokacin da yake koyar da darussan leken asiri na Inglish.
An kira Turanci zuwa Whitehall don yin la'akari, yana sake haɗuwa da tsohon mataimakinsa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga shi.
Bough yanzu ya zama miji mai aure wanda ke da dangantaka da kwamandan jirgin ruwa mai saukar ungulu mai farin ciki amma ɗan gajiya wanda Vicki Pepperdine ya buga.
Don haka Batman da Robin na ƙungiyar sirrin sarautar sarauniya sun dawo cikin aiki, suna haɗuwa da kyakkyawar mace mai ban mamaki Ophelia Bulletova, halin da Olga Kurylenko ta yi.
A halin yanzu, firaministan kasar ya shawo kan wani mai karfin hali, mai karfin kudi, mai amfani da fasaha, wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Birtaniya.
Turanci da Bough sun fara aikin su na rashin hankali: masu ba da sabis suna cin wuta a gidan abinci na Faransa; suna haifar da rikici ta hanyar shiga cikin jirgin ruwa na Volta; kuma Turanci yana lalata yayin amfani da kayan aikin gaskiya don ganin cikin gidan Volta.
A wannan lokacin, duk wani abin da aka hana shi ya ɓace, duk da cewa yana da kyau kuma yana da kyau, duk fim ɗin yana kama da talabijin na yara.
Ya kasance mai tsaka-tsaki.
Kamar yadda na yi a wasu fina-finai na Johnny English, na yi tunani cewa, shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da ta dace da baiwarsa ba?
Jam'iyyar Labour ta musanta cewa tana shirin samar da makonni hudu na aiki ga 'yan Birtaniya, inda za a biya su albashi a cikin kwanaki biyar.
Jam'iyyar Jeremy Corbyn ta Labour za ta yi la'akari da gabatar da wani tsari mai ban mamaki wanda zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako, kuma a biya su albashi na kwana biyar.
A cewar rahotanni, jam'iyyar ta ce tana son shugabannin kamfanoni su bai wa ma'aikata karin ranar hutu daga aikin da suka samu daga fasahar kere kere.
Hakan zai sa ma'aikata su yi hutu na kwana uku a mako kuma su sami albashi iri ɗaya.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayi zai dace da shirin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin da kasar ke yi na fuskantar ma'aikata.
An amince da yin aiki na kwana hudu a mako a majalisar kwadago a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata za su yi amfani da shi don canza tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa: "Ana sa ran za a sanar da sauyin manufofin kafin karshen wannan shekarar".
Ba za a yi wannan ba cikin dare daya, amma aikin kwana hudu ya zama wani abu da jam'iyyar ta ke so ta yi domin dawo da tattalin arziki cikin sauki ga ma'aikata, da kuma tsarin masana'antu na jam'iyyar.
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce jam'iyyar farko da ta goyi bayan wannan ra'ayin ba  Jam'iyyar Green Party ta yi alkawarin yin aiki na kwana hudu a mako a lokacin yakin neman zabe na 2017.
Amma a yanzu, ba duk 'yan jam'iyyar Labour ke goyon bayan wannan shirin ba.
Wani kakakin jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Ba siyasa ce ta jam'iyyarmu ta kafa mako na kwana hudu ba kuma ba ta tunanin yin hakan".
