Mene ne bikin 'yan kasa na duniya kuma shin ya taimaka wajen rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar mai zuwa, za a yi bikin Global Citizen Festival a birnin New York, wani biki na kiɗa na shekara-shekara da ke nuna manyan taurari da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa ta kawar da talauci a duniya.
A karo na bakwai, bikin na Global Citizen Festival zai tara dubban mutane da ke zuwa babban filin shakatawa na Central Park don su ji daɗin wasan kwaikwayon Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes, da kuma tallafawa babban burin taron, wanda shine kawar da talauci ta 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012 wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ce ta kasa da kasa da ke yaki da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikitin kyauta zuwa taron (sai dai idan sun zaɓi sayan tikitin VIP), masu halartar wasan kwaikwayon dole ne su yi aiki ko ayyuka da yawa, kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa shugaban duniya, yin kira, ko wasu ayyuka masu mahimmanci don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da manufar kawar da talauci.
Amma menene Global Citizen za ta samu a cikin shekaru 12 da suka rage?
Shin kyautar kyauta kyauta ce hanya mai kyau ta lallashe mutane su yi aiki, ko kuma wani misali ne na abin da ake kira "clicktivism" inda mutane ke jin cewa suna yin wani abu mai mahimmanci ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takardar neman taimako ta yanar gizo ko sanya tweet?
Kungiyar Global Citizen ta ce tun daga shekarar 2011, ta samu sama da mutane miliyan 19 da suka ba da gudummawarsu don cimma manufofi daban-daban.
Ya kuma ce waɗannan ayyukan sun taimaka wajen sa shugabannin duniya su yi alkawari da kuma kafa dokokin da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayukan mutane fiye da biliyan biyu da ɗari biyar a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta ambata alkawura 390 da kuma sanarwar da ta samu daga ayyukanta, wanda a kalla dala biliyan 10 aka biya ko aka biya.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa an riga an yi wa mutane kusan miliyan 649 a duniya allurar rigakafin.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya ta Birtaniya da ke hada masu zuba jari da masu sana'a da ke da sha'awar taimaka wa yara su cimma burinsu, wadda ta yi alkawarin ba da dala miliyan 35 don taimakawa Rwanda wajen magance matsalar karancin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan da mambobin Global Citizen suka wallafa tweets sama da 4,700.
Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasa da kuma 'yan Global Citizen kamar ku, za mu iya kawo ƙarshen rashin adalci na zamantakewa kamar rashin abinci mai gina jiki  Tracey Ullman, jakadan Power of Nutrition, yayin wasan kwaikwayo a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan da aka gudanar da ayyuka sama da 5,000 da ke kira ga Birtaniya da ta inganta ingancin abinci mai gina jiki ga uwaye da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da bayar da tallafi ga shirin Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 da ke fama da matsalar rashin abinci mai gina jiki.
A kan wata tambaya da aka fi yi a shafinsa, wadda ta ce, "Me ya sa za mu iya tabbata cewa za mu iya kawar da talauci?"
Global citizen ta amsa da cewa: "Wannan hanya ce mai tsawo da wahala, kuma za mu yi tuntuɓe da rashin nasara a wasu lokatai.
Amma kamar yadda ya faru a lokacin manyan ƙungiyoyin kare hakkin bil'adama da kuma yaƙi da wariyar launin fata, za mu yi nasara domin muna da ƙarfi tare.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe suna cikin fitattun jaruman da za su yi wasa a taron da za a yi a birnin New York a wannan shekara, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su karbi bakuncin.
