An ce taron Trump da Rosenstein zai sake jinkirta, a cewar fadar White House
An yi tsammanin za a jinkirta wani babban taron da Donald Trump zai yi da mataimakin babban lauyan kasar Rod Rosenstein har na mako guda saboda yakin da ake yi kan takarar babban alkalin kotun kolin Amurka, Brett Kavanaugh, a cewar fadar White House a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein yana kula da aikin da mai gabatar da kara na musamman Robert Mueller ke yi, wanda ke binciken yiwuwar Rasha ta tsoma baki a zaben, alakar da ke tsakanin manyan abokan aikin Trump da Rasha, da kuma yiwuwar hana shugaban aiwatar da shari'a.
Ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauyan kasar, wanda hakan zai shafi 'yancin Mueller, ya kasance babban batu a Washington tsawon watanni.
A farkon wannan watan jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna batun sanya waya don rikodin tattaunawar da Trump, da kuma yiwuwar cire shugaban daga mukaminsa a karkashin Kwaskwarima ta 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta wannan labarin.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata, ya je fadar White House, inda aka samu rahotanni cewa zai yi murabus.
An shirya ganawar da Trump, wanda ke zaune a hedkwatar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York, a ranar Alhamis.
Trump ya ce ba zai bar Rosenstein ba, amma an sake shirya taron ne don kauce wa rikici da sauraron shari'ar majalisar dattijai, inda Kavanaugh da wata mata da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin mata, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, suka ba da shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya ba da umarnin gudanar da binciken FBI na mako guda game da zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh, wanda hakan ya kara jinkirta kuri'ar majalisar dattijai.
Mai magana da yawun Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta bayyana a ranar Lahadi a Fox News.
Lokacin da aka tambaye ta game da ganawar da Rosenstein, ta ce: "Ba a riga an tsara ranar wannan ganawar ba, amma za a iya yin ta a wannan makon, ko kuma za a iya sake ta mako guda, idan aka yi la'akari da duk abubuwan da suka faru a Kotun Koli.
Za mu ga, zan sanar da manema labarai.
Wasu 'yan jarida sun yi tambaya game da wannan bayanin: Sanders ba ta yi taron manema labarai ba tun ranar 10 ga watan Satumba.
Mai gabatar da shirin, Chris Wallace, ya tambaye mu dalilin da ya sa hakan yake faruwa.
Sanders ta ce karancin taron manema labarai ba saboda rashin son 'yan jaridar talabijin masu nuna girman kai ba ne, ta kara da cewa: "Ba zan boye cewa su masu nuna girman kai ne ba".
Ta kuma ce za a kara samun hulda kai tsaye tsakanin Trump da 'yan jarida.
Shugaban da ke kan mulki yanzu yana gudanar da karin tambayoyi da amsoshi fiye da kowane shugaba da ya gabata,  in ji ta, ta kara da cewa ba tare da bayar da hujja ba,  mun san alkaluman .
Sanders ta ce za a ci gaba da gudanar da taron manema labarai, amma idan 'yan jarida za su iya tambayar shugaban Amurka kai tsaye, to hakan ya fi dacewa da su yi magana da ni.
Muna kokarin yin hakan a kai a kai, kuma mun yi hakan sau da yawa a cikin 'yan makonnin nan, taron manema labarai zai maye gurbin zaman tattaunawa da shugaban Amurka kai tsaye.
