Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da birnin Palu da kuma babban birnin Donggala a tsibirin Celebes:
Palu babban birnin Celebes ta Tsakiya ne, lardin da ke ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙaramin bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafa shi.
Donggala wani kabupaten ne (ƙungiyar gudanarwa a ƙasa da lardin) wanda ke kan iyakar arewa maso yammacin tsibirin tsawon kilomita 300.
An kiyasta cewa a shekara ta 2017, mazauna birnin 299,200 ne.
Babban fannonin tattalin arzikin Celebes ta Tsakiya shine kamun kifi da noma, waɗanda suka bunkasa musamman a garin Donggala da ke bakin teku.
Wata hanyar samun kudin shiga ta lardin ita ce ma'adinan nickel, amma galibi suna Morowali, a gefen gabar teku na Celebes.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta ƙasar Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a wurare da yawa a birnin Palau da Donggala.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami da ya auku a Donggala ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje.
A shekara ta 1996, mutane tara sun mutu a tsunami da ya auku a Donggala ta yamma.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin tekun Fasifik, kuma hakan yana sa a yi girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi girma a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa ta auku a lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afka wa kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya auku a gabar teku ta kudu, kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 kusa da birnin Padang, a yammacin Sumatra.
A sakamakon haka, mutane fiye da 1,100 sun mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da tekun Sumatra, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa da ba ta kai ruwa ba ta afku a garin Pidie Jaya da ke lardin Aceh, ta haddasa barna da firgici a tsakanin mutanen da ke ci gaba da tunawa da bala'in da girgizar kasa da tsunami ta 2004 ta yi.
Amma, ginin da ya rushe ya kashe mutane fiye da 100.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Sun halaka gidaje dubbai kuma sun jawo wa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido matsala na ɗan lokaci.
An kama babban dan Sara Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin mata
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, Sarah Palin, an kama shi da laifin hari.
A cewar rahoton da 'yan sanda suka fitar a ranar Asabar, an kama wani mutum mai shekara 29 daga garin Wasilla, Alaska, da laifin cin zarafin mata da maza da kuma hana bayar da rahoto da kuma adawa da kama shi.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya nuna cewa, lokacin da wata abokiyar wanda ake zargin ta yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda don kai rahoton aikata laifi, sai suka kwace wayar ta.
Hukumar KTUU ta ce Palin tana hannun hukuma a gidan Mat-Su kuma an ba ta belin dala 500.
Ta ce a ranar Asabar da ta gabata ne ya bayyana a gaban kotu inda ya bayyana rashin laifinsa.
Palin yana da laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin cewa zai iya fuskantar hukuncin daurin shekara guda da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ake kira Class B, wanda zai iya jawo hukuncin daurin kwana ɗaya a kurkuku da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka tuhumi Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an tuhume shi da laifin kai hari kan mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Sai mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don kai rahoton harin.
Yanzu haka dai, wannan shari'a tana gaban kotun Alaska ta kare hakkin soja.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata laifukan tashin hankali a gida, hana bayar da rahoto da kuma mallakar makami yayin da yake bugu dangane da wannan lamari.
Abokin aikinsa ya ce ya buge ta a fuska.
A shekara ta 2016, wasu kungiyoyin masu gwagwarmaya sun soki Sarah Palin, wadda ta danganta halin ɗanta na faɗa da ciwon damuwa da ya samu a lokacin da yake aiki a Iraki.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsunami bayan girgizar kasa a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da ta afku a tsibirin Celebes na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta haddasa tsunami kuma ta halaka dubban gidaje.
Ba a samun wutar lantarki da sadarwa kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu a kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta afku ne a kusa da tsibirin Celebes da ke arewa maso gabashin babban birnin kasar Indonesia, Jakarta.
Wasu bidiyoyi da ke nuna lokacin da bala'in ya auku sun bazu a shafukan sada zumunta.
Sa'ad da tsunami ya auko bakin teku, akwai mutane da yawa a bakin rairayin bakin teku a birnin Palu, inda ake bikin.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun bukaci a yankewa wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York hukuncin kisa.
Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun bukaci a yankewa Sayful Saipov hukuncin kisa a kan wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York da ya kashe mutane takwas, hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba tun shekarar 1953.
A cikin wani hari da aka kai a watan Oktoba a kan hanyar keke da ke kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, an ce Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot, wanda ya kori masu tafiya da kekuna a kan hanyarsa.
A cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar a gundumar kudu ta birnin New York, don tabbatar da cewa hukuncin kisa ya zama dole, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi mummunan rauni.
A cewar takardun kotu, za a kashe su a kan waɗannan laifuffuka biyu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta gabatar da wani hukunci kan Saipov da ya kunshi abubuwa 22, ciki har da laifuka takwas na kisan kai a cikin aikin da ba a yarda da shi ba  wanda shine tsarin da ake amfani da shi a cikin masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a cikin laifukan aikata laifuka  da kuma cin zarafi da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce shirya harin ya bukaci "tsarin tunani da kuma tsari" kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai harin a matsayin "mummunan, mummunan aiki da kuma lalata".
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya jawo wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleaves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlija, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damiano Pagnucca rauni, lalacewa da asarar abokai da dangi  sanarwar niyyar ta ce.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan kasar Argentina ne da ke birnin New York domin yawon bude ido.
Shekaru goma da suka shige ne aka yi shari'ar kisa a gundumar kudu ta birnin New York.
An samu wanda ake tuhuma Khalid Barnes da laifin kisan wasu 'yan dillalan miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma a karshe an yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
An kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg a New York a shekara ta 1953 bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa a shekara biyu da suka gabata saboda yin tawaye da kuma leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War.
An kashe Rosenberg da kuma Rosenberg a kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, wanda asalinsa Uzbekistan ne, bai nuna wani laifi ba a cikin watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi.
A cewar tuhumar, Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa bidiyon ISIS da ya kalli a wayar sa ne ya sa ya kai harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya bukaci a saka tutar ISIS a dakin jinya.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhuma guda 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin lauyoyin tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun yi takaicin matakin da mai gabatar da kara ya dauka.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke hukuncin kisa da kuma hana hukuncin rai da rai ba tare da samun damar samun 'yanci ba bayan ya amsa laifinsa zai kara wa duk wadanda abin ya shafa wahala", in ji shi.
A baya, 'yan lauyoyin Saipov sun nemi masu gabatar da kara da su daina neman hukuncin kisa.
'Yan majalisa na Tory sun ce Nigel Farage ya kamata ya dauki nauyin tattaunawar Brexit
A wani zanga-zanga da aka yi a yau a babban taron 'yan majalisa, Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin cewa zai tura sojojin jama'a.
Tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar United Kingdom Independence Party (UKIP) ya ce 'yan siyasa dole ne su ji zafi daga masu shakkar Turai lokacin da wani dan majalisa na Theresa May ya nuna cewa ya kamata ya dauki alhakin tattaunawa da Tarayyar Turai.
Dan majalisa mai wakiltar jam'iyyar Conservative, Peter Bone, ya shaida wa masu zanga-zanga a Birmingham cewa da a ce Farage ne sakataren Brexit, "Kasar Ingila za ta kasance a waje da Tarayyar Turai".
Amma, kasancewa tare da 'yan Tory masu goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a cikin al'umma a cikin zanga-zangar da aka yi a birnin, ya kara nuna nauyin da Theresa May ke fuskanta na sulhunta bangarorin da suka rabu.
Firaministan kasar na fama da wahalar aiwatar da shirin sulhunta da Chequers a yayin da ake fuskantar hare-hare daga masu goyon bayan Brexit, da masu adawa da shi, da kuma Tarayyar Turai kanta.
Abokan hulɗarta sun ce duk da ƙalubalen da za ta fuskanta, za ta yi aiki don cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels kuma ta tilasta wa masu shakkar Turai da ma'aikatanta su zabi tsakanin shawararta da "hargitsi".
Peter Bone ya shaida wa taron Leave Means Leave a Solihull cewa yana son a yi watsi da shirin Chequers.
Ya ce ya kamata a ba Nigel Farage alhakin gudanar da shawarwari da Brussels.
"Idan shi ne ya ke kula da wannan, da mun riga mun fita daga cikin Tarayyar Turai", in ji shi.
Wani dan majalisa daga Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Ina goyon bayan Brexit, amma dole ne mu fitar da shirin daga Chequers".
Da yake nuna rashin amincewarsa da Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: "Ba don mu yi yaƙi a yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya ba ne, don mu zama bayin wani.
Muna son mu yi mulki a kasarmu.
Peter Bone ya yi watsi da cewa 'yan kasar sun sauya tunaninsu tun bayan zaben 2016: "Tunanin cewa 'yan Birtaniya sun sauya tunaninsu kuma suna son ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin kungiyar EU ba gaskiya bane".
A lokacin zanga-zangar akwai kuma mai goyon bayan Brexit Andrea Jenkyns na jam'iyyar Tory, wadda ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina cewa ne: Madam firaminista, ku saurari jama'a.
Shirin Chequers ba shi da goyon bayan jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su kada kuri'a a kansa ba, jam'iyyarmu da masu fafutukarmu da ke zaune a kan tituna da suka zabe mu ba su da goyon baya.
Ka yi watsi da shirin da muke da shi na Chequers kuma ka soma saurarawa.
A wata sanarwa da ta yi wa Firaminista May, ta kara da cewa: "Firai ministoci suna ci gaba da yin abin da suka yi alkawari".
Nigel Farage ya ce 'yan siyasa da ke zanga-zangar dole ne su "ji zafi" idan za su yi watsi da shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
"Yanzu batun amana ne tsakanin mu da 'yan siyasa", in ji shi.
Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit, kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu cewa ba za mu bari ku yi hakan ba.
Da yake magana da taron masu farin ciki, ya kara da cewa, "Ina so ku sa 'yan siyasa da ke kan iyakar cin amanar Brexit su ji zafi.
"Muna tattara sojojin mutanen wannan kasa da suka ba mu nasara a kuri'ar raba gardamar Brexit, kuma ba za mu huta ba har sai mun zama 'yanci, masu zaman kansu, masu alfahari da Burtaniya".
A lokacin ne masu adawa da ficewar Birtaniya suka yi gangami zuwa cikin gari inda suka yi zanga-zangar tsawon awa biyu.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya sun yi amfani da tutar "Tory a kan Brexit" bayan kafa kungiyar a karshen mako.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Labour, Baron Andrew Adonis, ya yi wa 'yan majalisa ba'a kan matsalar tsaro a cikin manhajar jam'iyyar a farkon taron.
"Waɗannan mutane ne da ke da'awar cewa za su iya tsara tsarin IT da duk fasahar don tallafawa shirin Kanada da ƙari, iyakar da ba ta da iyaka, cinikayya ba tare da iyaka ba tare da Ireland ba".
Wannan ba gaskiya ba ne.
Babu wani abu kamar kyakkyawar Brexit", in ji shi.
Elizabeth Warren ta yi niyyar yin la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa.
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A cewar jaridar Boston Globe, wata 'yar majalisar wakilai ta Massachusetts ta bayyana makomar ta a wani taron masu jefa kuri'a da aka yi a yammacin Massachusetts a ranar Asabar.
Elizabeth Warren, wacce ta saba sukar shugaba Donald Trump, za ta sake tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa a watan Nuwamba, tana karawa da wakilin jam'iyyar Republican Geoff Diehl, wanda ya jagoranci yakin neman zaben Trump a Massachusetts a zaben 2016.
A yanzu haka, ana ta cewa Warren na iya doke Trump a zaben 2020.
Taron da ta yi a garin Holyoke a ranar Asabar shi ne karo na 36 da ta gana da masu jefa kuri'a a zauren majalisar tun lokacin da Donald Trump ya hau mulki.
Wani daga cikin masu halartar taron ya tambaye ni ko zan yi takarar shugaban kasa.
Elizabeth Warren ta ce lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington don gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace.
An kama wanda ya yi wannan mummunan harbi da ya kashe dan wasan LSU, Wayde Sims
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge, Louisiana sun ce sun kama wani da ake zargi da harbin bindiga da ya kashe dan wasan kwando na LSU Wayde Sims a ranar Juma'a.
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge sun ce an kama wani mutum mai shekaru 20 mai suna Dyton Simpson a wani taron manema labarai da aka yi da misalin karfe 11:00 na yammacin kasar.
A ranar Juma'a, an wallafa wani bidiyo na harbi da aka yi da wani mutum da aka nuna a hoton.
Wayde Sims, mai shekara 20, an kashe shi ne a wani harbi da aka yi masa a wani yanki kusa da jami'ar Southern a safiyar ranar Juma'a.
"Wayde Sims ya ji rauni ne sakamakon harbin bindiga da aka yi masa a kai, wanda ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwarsa", in ji shugaban 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul a wata sanarwa da 247sports ta fitar.
Wayde ya kare abokinsa kuma Simpson ya harbe shi.
An yi wa Simpson tambayoyi kuma ya furta cewa ya kasance a wurin kisan, yana da makami kuma ya harbe Wayde.
Bayan an kama shi, kuma bai yi tsayayya ba, an kai shi ofishin 'yan sanda na yankin Baton Rouge.
Wayde Sims, dan wasa mai tsayi 1,98 m, ya girma a Baton Rouge, kuma ya buga wasanni 32 da farawa 10 a kakar wasa ta ƙarshe, inda ya yi kimanin minti 17.4 a filin wasa, ya ci 5.6 da kuma 2.9 a kowane wasa.
Lewis Hamilton ya kusa lashe gasar cin kofin duniya bayan da ya lashe gasar da Sebastian Vettel
Tun lokacin da Valtteri Bottas ya yi tseren tsere da Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar, ya bayyana cewa umarnin da Mercedes ta ba shi zai yi tasiri sosai a sakamakon tseren.
Bottas, wanda ya fara daga filin farko, ya fara da kyau kuma ya kusan doke Hamilton, yana kare matsayinsa a cikin zagaye biyu na farko kuma ya tilasta Vettel ya kai wa abokin aikinsa hari.
Vettel ne ya fara zuwa wurin da ake ba da sabis ɗin kuma ya bar Hamilton ya bi bayan sa, wanda ya kamata ya yanke shawarar ƙarshen tseren.
Mai tseren Mercedes ya sauka a cikin jirgi na gaba kuma ya bayyana a bayan Vettel, amma bayan aikin da ya yi a cikin zagaye wanda ya sa direban Ferrari ya ƙi barin cikin filin, yana fuskantar fuskantar turawa zuwa tsaro bayan motsi biyu na abokin hamayyarsa don kare matsayin a cikin kwana na uku, Hamilton ya hau kan gaba.
Max Verstappen ya fara daga ƙarshen tseren kuma a ranar haihuwarsa ta 21 a ƙarshen zagaye na farko ya kasance na bakwai.
Daga nan sai ya jagoranci mafi yawan tseren ta hanyar ba tare da canza tayoyin ba don yin saurin gamawa da kuma karɓar Kimi Raikkonen matsayi na huɗu.
Daga karshe ya sauka zuwa wurin da ake amfani da shi a zagaye na 44, amma a sauran zagaye takwas da suka rage bai samu saurin gudu ba.
"Yau rana ce mai wuya, domin a duk ƙarshen mako Valtteri ya yi aiki mai kyau kuma ya nuna cewa shi mutum ne mai kirki sa'ad da aka ce ya ƙyale ni in wuce.
"Dukan 'yan wasan sun yi iya ƙoƙarinsu don su ci gaba da zama a kan gaba", in ji Hamilton.
Wannan mummunan magana ce ta jiki.
A wani taron da suka yi a ranar Asabar, Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi tir da Sanata Dianna Feinstein, wacce ta yi ikirarin cewa ba ta bayyana sakon da ta rubuta daga Christina Blasey Ford ba, inda ta zargi mai shari'a Brett Kavanaugh da cin zarafin mata.
Da yake jawabi ga wani taro a jihar West Virginia, shugaban bai yi magana kai tsaye game da shaidar da Christina Ford ta bayar a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai ba, amma ya ce abin da ya faru a majalisar dattijai ya nuna cewa mutane "masu ƙeta, masu ƙeta, da masu ƙarya".
"Abin da zai iya faruwa abu daya ne, amma wannan kyakkyawan yanayin a majalisar dattijai da muke gani a cikin 'yan kwanakin nan, lokacin da muke ganin fushi, lokacin da muke ganin mutane masu fushi, masu banƙyama, masu banƙyama da maƙaryaci", in ji shi.
"Muna ganin abin da aka buga da kuma fallasa, sannan kuma suna gaya mana, 'Wow, ban yi ba.'
Ba ni na yi wannan ba.
Ka tuna da shi?
Dianna Feinstein, shin ka bayyana wannan?
Ku tuna da amsar da ta bayar... kun bayyana abinda ke cikin wannan takardar?
Oh, ba haka ba.
Ban bayyana mata ba.
Ka ɗan jira.
"Shin mun bayyana... A'a, ba mu bayyana ba", in ji shi, yana mai gargadi ga Sanata.
Dianna Feinstein ta samu wasiƙar daga Christina Ford da ke bayyana zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh a watan Yuli, kuma an fallasa ta a farkon watan Satumba.
"Ban ɓoye abin da Dr. Ford ta yi ba, ban bayyana labarinta ba", in ji Feinstein a gaban kwamitin, kamar yadda jaridar The Hill ta ruwaito.
Ta ce in yi shiru, kuma na bi ta, ban bayyana abin da ke ciki ba.
Amma, wannan ba ta gamsar da shugaban kasa ba, wanda ya yi sharhi a kan wannan a taron ranar Asabar: "Ina gaya muku, wannan mummunan magana ne.
Wataƙila ba ta yi hakan ba, amma wannan shi ne mafi munin magana da jiki da na taɓa gani.
A yayin da yake ci gaba da kare dan takarar kotun koli wanda mata uku suka zargi da cin zarafin mata, shugaban ya nuna cewa 'yan Democrat suna amfani da wannan zargi don amfanin kansu.
Sun ƙudura aniyar karɓar mulki ta kowane hali.
"Suna nuna wulakanci, da ƙeta, ba su damu da wanda suke cutarwa ba, wanda dole ne su hallaka don samun iko da iko", in ji shugaban, kamar yadda Mediaite ta ruwaito.
Ƙungiyar Elite: Dundee Stars  Belfast Giants 5:3
A wasan da suka buga da Dundee, Patrick Dwyer ya ci wa Giants biyu.
Dundee Stars sun biya diyyar rashin nasarar da suka sha a gasar Elite League da Belfast Giants ranar Juma'a, inda suka ci wasan da suka yi a gida da kashi 5 da 3 a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun samu nasara da sauri da tazarar raga biyu daga hannun Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita, sannan Dwyer ya sake fitar da Giants domin su ci gaba.
Francois Bouchard ya sake daidaita wasan, inda ya ci wa Dundee kwallo, sannan kuma kwallo biyu da Lucas Lundwald Nielsen ya zira sun tabbatar da nasarar.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na uku da kungiyar ta yi rashin nasara a gasar Elite League a bana a hannun Adam Keefe, wanda duk da rashin nasarar da suka sha a ranar Juma'a da yamma, suka ci Dundee a Belfast da ci 2-1.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na hudu da kungiyoyin biyu ke karawa a bana.
Dwyer ya fara wasan ne a minti na hudu (3:35) bayan da Kendall McFaul ya taimaka masa.
Bayan da aka fara wasa da karfi a karfe 13:10 Sullivan ya dawo da 'yan wasan gida, sannan Matt Marquardt ya daidaita a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun ci gaba da cin nasara a wasan farko na wasan, lokacin da ya ci kwallo ta biyu a wasan.
An sake tsara 'yan wasan gida kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaita sakamakon da aka samu a wasan da aka yi a cikin minti 27:37.
A ƙarshen kashi na biyu, Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun taimaka wa Nielsen don ba wa Dundee damar samun nasara a wasan.
