Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018, ta doke Amurka da 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a filin wasa na Le Golf National a bayan birnin Paris.
A ƙasar Turai, Amirka ta yi rashin nasara a karo na shida a jere kuma ba ta taɓa lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun shekara ta 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe gasar ne a lokacin da ta samu maki 14.5 da ta bukaci a doke Amurka.
Tauraron kwallon kafa na Amurka, Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a gasar, ya buga kwallon daga cikin kwando zuwa cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na PAR3, ya ba da wasan ga Francesco Molinari.
Molinari ɗan Italiya ya yi wasa a duk zagaye kuma ya zama ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasan golf huɗu da suka ci 5-0-0 tun daga 1979, lokacin da aka fara gasar a wannan tsarin.
An kori Jordan Spieth na Amurka da ci 5 da 4 daga hannun Thorbjørn Olesen na Denmark, dan wasan da ya fi kasa a Turai.
Dustin Johnson, wanda shi ne babban dan wasa a duniya, ya rasa rami biyu kafin rami na karshe da dan wasan Ingila Ian Poulter, wanda watakila wannan shine gasar Ryder Cup ta karshe.
