Bayanan Fure  a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota, yawan plankton yana raguwa
Wani rahoto daga Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa yawan tsuntsayen da ke cikin teku sun ragu a wasu yankunan da ke yankin Tampa Bay.
Hukumar ta ce an samu wasu 'yan fashi a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma Collier, kuma hakan ya nuna cewa yawan su yana raguwa.
Tana da nisan mil 130 daga arewacin jihar Pinellas zuwa kudancin jihar Lee.
Ana iya samun waɗannan ƙwayoyin a kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma a wurare kaɗan fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga wani fure a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an samu matsakaicin yawan plankton a bakin tekun da kuma ruwan Pinellas County, low zuwa matsakaici a bakin tekun Hillsborough County, na halitta zuwa high a cikin Manatee County, na halitta zuwa high a bakin tekun da ruwan Sarasota County, na halitta zuwa matsakaici a cikin Charlotte County, na halitta zuwa high a bakin tekun da ruwan Lee County, da kuma low a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni na ciwon huhu a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Amma a makon da ya gabata, babu wani abu da aka samu a arewa maso yammacin Florida.
